# Bakery Website Template

A simple and responsive bakery-themed website built using:

- HTML  
- CSS  
- JavaScript

## Features

- Homepage with hero section and welcome message  
- Product showcase section for featured bakery items  
- Contact form with basic structure  
- Responsive layout for mobile and desktop  
- Clean, organized code structure for easy editing

## Purpose

This project was created to practice front-end development skills  
It can be reused or adapted for small business websites, especially bakeries

## Live Demo

View the website here:  
[https://marwaelgorn.github.io/bakery/](https://marwaelgorn.github.io/bakery/)
